        <RadzenText Text="From 2009 to 2013 at Technology and Systems Department, MINCOM, Havana, Cuba" TextStyle="TextStyle.H6"/>
        <RadzenText Text="My first work was in a datacenter, involved maintaining and troubleshooting the hardware and software systems that store and process large amounts of data. As a specialist also perform tasks such as installing new equipment, configuring network settings, monitoring performance and security, and updating software. A datacenter I developed strong technical skills, problem-solving abilities, and attention to detail."/>

