        <RadzenText Text="From 2013 to 2015 at Metropolitan Bank, attached to the Central Bank of Cuba, Havana, Cuba" TextStyle="TextStyle.H6"/>
        <RadzenText Text="At the bank I was responsible for setting up, managing and troubleshooting the technology systems that the bank uses to operate and serve its customers. Also implement security measures to protect the bank's data and network from cyberattacks. And provide technical support to bank staff and help them use the software and hardware efficiently. Plus keep track of the technology costs and update the systems as needed."/>

