        <RadzenText Text="As a specialist in a CERT, I was responsible for responding to cyber incidents and providing technical support to prevent or mitigate cyber-attacks. Performed tasks such as analyzing malware, conducting digital forensics, monitoring network traffic, managing security tools, and coordinating with other stakeholders."/>

